videos.headline: Fresno State TE dives into end zone to extend lead
videos.description: Kyle Riddering dives for a score, giving Fresno State a 13-0 lead.

videos.headline: UCLA answers with 45-yard TD
videos.description: UCLA QB Dorian Thompson-Robinson fires a 45-yard missile to WR Theo Howard to cut deficit to 16-7.

videos.headline: Snapper recovers muffed punt, leads to TD after
videos.description: UCLA snapper Johnny Den Bleyker races down the field to recover a fumbled punt, leading to a touchdown run three plays later.

videos.headline: Fresno State QB sneaks it in for TD
videos.description: Fresno State QB Marcus McMAryion sneaks in the end zone for a TD.
